{"tid":308470,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(今晚唔知 00:10 定 01:10) (蔣嘉琦有份參賽) 國際女騎師邀請賽","createTime":"2017-07-04T07:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T05:30:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68dad5a1c658560bf19037b33a8e6fdbe3ec30b2","tid":308470,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:40:38.000Z","msg":"(今晚唔知 00:10 定 01:10)<br />\n(蔣嘉琦有份參賽) Lady Jockeys&rsquo; Thoroughbred World Championship <br />\n<br />\n9 個受邀請女騎師鬥5場, 計分賽<br />\n每場名次各得以下分數<br />\n<br />\n名次 - 得分<br />\n1 - 15<br />\n2 - 12<br />\n3 - 10<br />\n4 - 7<br />\n5 - 4<br />\n6 - 2<br />\n7 - 2<br />\n8 - 2<br />\n9 - 2<br />\n退出 - 5<br />\n<br />\n監場董事覺得個場有人犯規 有權扣 5 分,  當日跑6場馬, 1, 2, 3, 4, 6 呢 5 場就係女騎師計分賽賽事. (即係第5場唔係)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當地 18:10 開跑第一場,  (香港時間唔知係 00:10 定 01:10)<br />\n當地 20:40 開跑第六場<br />\n<br />\nfacebook link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ljchampionship/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fljchampionship%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DPAGES_TIMELINE%26fref%3Dnf&d=rnN3sZUNEYpahFPz0GwFHwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a29ed899\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ljchampionship/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE&amp;fref=nf</a><br />\n<br />\n直播 link<br />\n<a href=\"http://cricbox.co/racing-uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcricbox.co%2Fracing-uk&d=rnN3sZUNEYpahFPz0GwFHwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=fde1e7bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://cricbox.co/racing-uk</a><br />\n<br />\n排位表<br />\n<a href=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5939f7b020099e5c3eaec88f/t/5956a475ebbd1aa05cbfcd65/1498850437885/Bro+170704+GB+Racecard.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F5939f7b020099e5c3eaec88f%2Ft%2F5956a475ebbd1aa05cbfcd65%2F1498850437885%2FBro%2B170704%2BGB%2BRacecard.pdf&d=rnN3sZUNEYpahFPz0GwFHwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=cecb3f43\" target=\"_blank\">https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5939f7b020099e5c3eaec88f/t/5956a475ebbd1aa05cbfcd65/1498850437885/Bro+170704+GB+Racecard.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"6455f5b1c81935af8f1adcf5c2ed4ccfac4e56b9","tid":308470,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:45:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ljchampionship/photos/a.170465063489433.1073741828.168781216991151/183798372156102/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fljchampionship%2Fphotos%2Fa.170465063489433.1073741828.168781216991151%2F183798372156102%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=rnN3sZUNEYpahFPz0GwFHwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=255e888b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ljchampionship/photos/a.170465063489433.1073741828.168781216991151/183798372156102/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\nLady Jockeys&rsquo; Thoroughbred World Championship<br />\n讚好此專頁 &middot; 7月2日 &middot; <br />\n <br />\nKei Chiong will represent Hong Kong in the Lady Jockeys' Thoroughbred World Championship at Bro Park in Sweden on Tuesday. Did you know she was the first female jockey to ride a four-timer in Hong Kong? Read more on <a href=\"http://www.ljtwc.com/kei-chiong/&mdash;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ljtwc.com%2Fkei-chiong%2F%E2%80%94&d=rnN3sZUNEYpahFPz0GwFHwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6a3ea210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ljtwc.com/kei-chiong/&mdash;</a> 標籤︰Ka Kei 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19656972_183798372156102_7428710641160712733_n.jpg?oh=552ead37accac830f2ffe8caaaba6892&amp;oe=59D0CB85\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19656972_183798372156102_7428710641160712733_n.jpg%3Foh%3D552ead37accac830f2ffe8caaaba6892%26oe%3D59D0CB85&h=efca7cb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae09319a2f5e54fa224d109b8077f20fe575afbf","tid":308470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r